Description: Provides tools to load, clean, analyze, and visualize student lifestyle and academic performance data. 
    The package focuses on relationships between variables such as sleep, study time, stress levels, and exam scores. 
    It enables users to explore patterns in student behavior, generate summary statistics, create visualizations, 
    and build simple predictive models to understand academic outcomes.
